cdata.name: Volpo
cdata.desc:
Volpo is an online platform for cryptocurrencies purchase. Its goal is to become a tool for the users to buy cryptocurrencies online, using fiat. Volpo users will be able to perform transactions between their local currency and VLP token as well as exchange the VLP tokens for their local currency.

The VLP token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency. It is a token designed to facilitate operations within the Volpo exchange, offering advantages in a form of discounts to its users.
